    <title>Macro Shocks and Firm-Level Response Heterogeneity</title>
    <updated>2025-06-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Steven J. Davis, Stephen Hansen &amp; Cristhian Seminario-Amez</name>
